  • Menus Press return or enter to open this panel

    • You are customizing Menus

      This panel is used for managing navigation menus for content you have already published on your site. You can create menus and add items for existing content such as pages, posts, categories, tags, formats, or custom links.

      Menus can be displayed in locations defined by your theme or in widget areas by adding a “Custom Menu” widget.

      Show advanced menu properties

    • Menu Locations Press return or enter to open this section

      • Customizing ▸ Menus Menu Locations

        Your theme supports 2 menus. Select which menu appears in each location.

        You can also place menus in widget areas with the Custom Menu widget.
